Title: Hard-boiled egg with a side of sliced grapefruit
Quantity: ["1 large egg, hard-boiled","1/2 grapefruit, sliced"]
RecipeMethod: ["Fill a small pot with water and place it over high heat to boil.","Once the water is boiling, carefully add the egg to the pot using a spoon or tongs.","Boil the egg for 8-10 minutes.","While the egg is boiling, slice the grapefruit in half and then slice one half into segments.","Once the egg is boiled, remove it from the pot using a spoon or tongs and place it in a bowl of cold water to cool.","Once the egg has cooled, peel off the shell.","Serve the hard-boiled egg with the sliced grapefruit on the side.","Enjoy!"]

Title: Mushroom and Spinach Frittata
Quantity: ["6 large eggs","1/2 cup chopped mushrooms","1/2 cup chopped spinach","1/4 cup diced onions","1 clove minced garlic","1 tablespoon olive oil","Salt and pepper to taste","1/4 cup shredded low-fat cheese"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).", "In a skillet over medium heat, add olive oil and cook mushrooms, spinach, onions, and garlic until tender, stirring occasionally.","In a separate bowl, whisk eggs and season with salt and pepper.","Add cooked vegetables to the egg mixture and mix well.","Pour the egg and vegetable mixture into a greased 8-inch baking dish.","Sprinkle shredded cheese on top.","Bake for 20-25 minutes or until the frittata is set and the cheese is melted", "Serve hot."]

Title: Black Bean and Sweet Potato Tacos
Quantity: ["2 medium sweet potatoes, peeled and cubed","1 tablespoon olive oil","1 can black beans, drained and rinsed","1/2 teaspoon ground cumin","1/4 teaspoon smoked paprika", "Salt and pepper, to taste","8 small corn tortillas"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).","Toss sweet potato cubes with olive oil and spread them out on a baking sheet. Bake for 20-25 minutes, or until tender and lightly browned.","While the sweet potatoes are baking, heat a can of black beans over medium heat in a saucepan. Add cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper to taste, and cook until heated through, stirring occasionally.","To assemble tacos, warm tortillas in a dry skillet over medium-high heat. Fill each tortilla with a scoop of black beans and a scoop of sweet potatoes. Add any toppings you desire.","Serve immediately and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["sweet potatoes","olive oil","black beans","ground cumin","smoked paprika", "Salt and pepper","corn tortillas"]

Title: Poached eggs with steamed asparagus
Quantity: ["2 large eggs","6-8 asparagus spears","1/2 tablespoon white vinegar","Salt and black pepper to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["Fill a large saucepan with 2 inches of water and bring to a gentle simmer over medium heat.Meanwhile, wash the asparagus spears and trim the tough ends.Once the water is simmering, add the white vinegar to the saucepan. Crack each egg into a small ramekin or cup.Gently slide each egg into the simmering water, one at a time.","Let the eggs cook for 3-4 minutes for a runny yolk, or 5-6 minutes for a firmer yolk. While the eggs are cooking, place the asparagus spears in a steamer basket and steam them for 3-5 minutes, until they are tender but still crisp.","Remove the asparagus from the steamer basket and season with salt and black pepper.Using a slotted spoon, remove the poached eggs from the water and place them on top of the steamed asparagus.Season the eggs with salt and black pepper.","Serve and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["eggs","asparagus spears","white vinegar","Salt and black pepper to taste"]

Title: Banana pancakes made with mashed bananas and egg whites
Quantity: ["1 large banana, mashed","2 egg whites","1/4 teaspoon vanilla extract","1/4 teaspoon cinnamon (optional)","Cooking spray or butter for the pan"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a medium bowl, mash the banana with a fork until it is mostly smooth.","Add the egg whites, vanilla extract, and cinnamon (if using) to the bowl with the mashed banana and whisk until the mixture is well combined.","Heat a nonstick skillet or griddle over medium heat and spray with cooking spray or melt butter to coat the pan.","Use a 1/4 cup measuring cup to pour the pancake batter onto the skillet.","Cook for 2-3 minutes, or until the edges start to set and the pancakes are golden brown on the bottom.","Use a spatula to flip the pancakes and cook for another 1-2 minutes, or until the other side is golden brown.","Repeat with the remaining batter, making sure to re-spray the skillet with cooking spray or add more butter between batches.","Serve the pancakes warm with your choice of toppings, such as fresh berries or a drizzle of honey."]

Title: Breakfast wrap with scrambled eggs
Quantity: ["2 egg whites","1/4 cup diced tomatoes","1 whole wheat wrap"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a bowl, whisk the egg whites until light and fluffy.","Heat a non-stick skillet over medium-high heat and spray with cooking spray.","Pour the egg whites into the skillet and scramble until fully cooked.","Add the diced tomatoes to the skillet and cook for 1-2 minutes, or until the tomatoes are slightly softened.","Place the cooked egg whites and tomatoes in the center of the whole wheat wrap.","Roll up the wrap tightly and slice in half, if desired.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Baked Falafel
Quantity: ["1 can chickpeas","1/4 cup chopped onion","2 cloves garlic","2 tbsp chopped parsley","1 tbsp lemon juice","1 tsp ground cumin","1 tsp ground coriander","1/2 tsp salt","1/4 tsp black pepper","2 tbsp whole wheat flour","2 tbsp olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat the oven to 375°F.","In a food processor, pulse the chickpeas, onion, garlic, parsley, lemon juice, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper until it forms a coarse mixture.","Add the flour to the mixture and pulse again to combine.","Form the mixture into small balls and flatten into patties.","Place the patties on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.","Brush each patty with olive oil.","Bake for 20 minutes, flip the patties over, and bake for an additional 10-15 minutes until golden brown."]

Title: Cottage cheese with sliced peaches and a few almonds
Quantity: ["1/2 cup low-fat cottage cheese","1 medium peach, sliced","1 tablespoon chopped almonds"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a bowl, add the low-fat cottage cheese.","Wash the peach, slice it into bite-sized pieces, and add it on top of the cottage cheese.","Sprinkle the chopped almonds on top.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Green smoothie made with spinach, banana, almond milk, and chia seeds
Quantity: ["2 cups fresh baby spinach",1 ripe banana, peeled and sliced","1 cup unsweetened almond milk","1 tablespoon chia seeds"]
RecipeMethod: ["Add the fresh baby spinach, sliced banana, almond milk, and chia seeds to a blender.","Blend all the ingredients until the mixture is smooth and creamy.","Pour the smoothie into a glass and serve."]

Title: Grilled Chicken Caesar Salad
Quantity: ["2 boneless, skinless chicken breasts","1 head of romaine lettuce","1/4 cup of grated parmesan cheese","1/2 cup of croutons","Caesar dressing (homemade or store-bought)","Salt and pepper","Olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat grill to medium-high heat.","Brush chicken with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.","Grill chicken for 6-8 minutes per side or until fully cooked.","Let the chicken rest for a few minutes, then slice into thin strips.","In a large bowl, combine chopped romaine lettuce, grated parmesan cheese, and croutons.","Add the grilled chicken to the bowl and toss everything together.","Drizzle with Caesar dressing and serve."]
Ingredients: ["chicken breasts","romaine lettuce","parmesan cheese","croutons","Caesar dressing","Salt and pepper","Olive oil"]

Title: Quinoa bowl with diced apples, cinnamon, and almond milk
Quantity: ["1/2 cup cooked quinoa","1 medium apple, diced","1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/2 cup unsweetened almond milk"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a small saucepan, warm up the cooked quinoa over low heat.","Add the diced apple to the saucepan and stir to combine.","Sprinkle the ground cinnamon on top of the mixture and stir to evenly distribute.","Pour the almond milk over the quinoa mixture and stir to combine.","Cook the mixture over low heat until the almond milk is absorbed and the quinoa is warm.","Transfer the mixture to a bowl and serve."]

Title: Whole wheat toast with almond butter and sliced banana
Quantity: ["1 slice of whole wheat bread","1 tablespoon almond butter","1/2 banana, sliced"]
RecipeMethod: ["Toast the slice of whole wheat bread to your desired level of crispiness.","Spread the almond butter on top of the toast.","Arrange the sliced banana on top of the almond butter.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Grilled Shrimp Salad
Quantity: ["1 lb large shrimp, peeled and deveined","2 tablespoons olive oil","1/2 teaspoon garlic powder","1/2 teaspoon smoked paprika","Salt and pepper, to taste","6 cups mixed greens","1 cup cherry tomatoes, halved","1 avocado, diced","1/4 red onion, thinly sliced","2 tablespoons chopped fresh parsley","2 tablespoons lemon juice","1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","1 tablespoon honey"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.","In a bowl, toss shrimp with olive oil, garlic powder, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper until well coated.","Grill shrimp for 2-3 minutes per side, or until cooked through and slightly charred.","In a large bowl, combine mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, avocado, red onion, and chopped parsley.","In a small bowl, whisk together lemon juice, Dijon mustard, honey, salt, and pepper to make the dressing.","Add the grilled shrimp to the salad, drizzle with dressing, and toss to combine.","Serve immediately."]
Ingredients: ["shrimps","olive oil","garlic powder","smoked paprika","Salt and pepper","tomato","avocado","red onion","parsley","lemon juice","Dijon mustard","honey"]

Title: Low-fat yogurt with granola and sliced strawberries
Quantity: ["1/2 cup low-fat plain yogurt","1/4 cup granola","4-5 sliced strawberries"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a bowl, add the low-fat plain yogurt.","Add the granola on top of the yogurt.","Arrange the sliced strawberries on top of the granola.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Baked Salmon with Roasted Brussels Sprouts
Quantity: ["4 fish fillets","1 tablespoon olive oil","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1/2 teaspoon garlic powder","1/2 teaspoon dried thyme","1/2 teaspoon paprika","1 lb Brussels sprouts","1 tablespoon balsamic vinegar","1 tablespoon honey"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).","Place the cod fillets in a baking dish.","Drizzle olive oil over the cod and sprinkle with salt, pepper, garlic powder, thyme, and paprika.","Arrange the halved Brussels sprouts around the cod fillets.","In a small bowl, whisk together the balsamic vinegar and honey.","Drizzle the balsamic-honey mixture over the Brussels sprouts.","Bake for 15-20 minutes, or until the cod is cooked through and the Brussels sprouts are tender.","Serve hot."]
Ingredients: ["fish fillets","olive oil","salt","black pepper","garlic powder","dried thyme","paprika","Brussels sprouts","balsamic vinegar","honey"]

Title: Mushroom and Spinach Quesadilla
Quantity: ["1 large whole wheat tortilla","1 cup sliced mushrooms","1 cup fresh spinach leaves","1/4 cup diced onion","1/4 cup shredded reduced-fat cheddar cheese","1 tablespoon olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a skillet over medium heat, add olive oil and diced onion. Cook until the onion is translucent.","Add sliced mushrooms to the skillet and cook until they are soft.

Title: Oatmeal with sliced bananas and a sprinkle of cinnamon
Quantity: ["1/2 cup rolled oats","1 cup water","1 medium banana, sliced","1/4 teaspoon ground cinnamon"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a small saucepan, combine the rolled oats and water.","Bring the mixture to a boil over medium-high heat, then reduce the heat to low.","Simmer the oats for about 5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the oats are tender and the water is absorbed.","Remove the saucepan from the heat and let it cool for a minute or two.","Divide the oatmeal into bowls and top with sliced bananas.","Sprinkle cinnamon on top of the bananas.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Turkey and Vegetables
Quantity: ["1 lb turkey breast, sliced into thin strips","2 tablespoons vegetable oil","1 red bell pepper, sliced","1 green bell pepper, sliced","1 small onion, sliced","2 cups broccoli florets","1 cup sliced mushrooms","1 teaspoon minced garlic","2 tablespoons low-sodium soy sauce","1 tablespoon cornstarch","1/2 cup low-sodium chicken broth","Salt and pepper, to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a large skillet or wok, heat vegetable oil over medium-high heat.","Add turkey strips and cook until browned on all sides, about 5-7 minutes. Remove from skillet and set aside.","Add red and green bell peppers, onion, broccoli, mushrooms, and garlic to the skillet. Cook until vegetables are tender-crisp, about 5-7 minutes.","In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, cornstarch, and chicken broth until well combined.","Return the turkey to the skillet with the vegetables, and pour the soy sauce mixture over everything.","Stir to combine and cook until the sauce has thickened, about 2-3 minutes.","Season with salt and pepper to taste.","Serve hot with brown rice or quinoa."]
Ingredients: ["turkey","vegetable oil","red bell pepper","green bell pepper","onion","broccoli florets", "mushrooms","garlic","soy sauce","cornstarch","chicken broth","Salt and pepper"]

Title: Grilled Chicken and Veggie Skewers
Quantity: ["1 lb. boneless, skinless chicken breast, cut into cubes","1 red bell pepper, cut into cubes","1 green bell pepper, cut into cubes","1 onion, cut into cubes","1 zucchini, sliced","1 yellow squash, sliced","Salt and pepper, to taste","Olive oil, for brushing","Skewers, soaked in water"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat grill to medium-high heat.","In a bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, minced garlic, honey, dried oregano, salt and pepper.","Thread chicken and vegetables onto skewers, alternating between chicken and veggies.","Brush skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.","Brush marinade onto the skewers, making sure to coat each piece.","Grill the skewers for about 10-15 minutes, turning occasionally, until chicken is cooked through and veggies are tender and slightly charred.","Serve hot and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["chicken breast","bell pepper","green bell pepper","onion","zucchini","yellow squash","Salt and pepper","Olive oil","Skewers"]

Title: Lentil Salad with Roasted Vegetables
Quantity: ["1 cup green lentils","3 cups mixed vegetables (such as cherry tomatoes, bell peppers, zucchini, and eggplant)","1 red onion, chopped","2 tablespoons olive oil","Salt and pepper, to taste","2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar","2 tablespoons Dijon mustard","1 tablespoon honey","1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley","1/4 cup crumbled feta cheese (optional)"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).","Rinse lentils and cook them in boiling water for 20-25 minutes, or until tender. Drain and set aside.","Toss chopped vegetables and onion with olive oil, salt, and pepper, and spread them out on a baking sheet. Roast for 20-25 minutes, or until tender and lightly browned.","In a small bowl, whisk together balsamic vinegar, Dijon mustard, honey, and a pinch of salt.","In a large bowl, combine cooked lentils, roasted vegetables, and chopped parsley. Drizzle with the balsamic dressing and toss to combine.","Sprinkle with crumbled feta cheese, if desired.","Serve immediately or refrigerate until ready to serve."]
Ingredients: ["green lentils","red onion","olive oil","Salt and pepper","balsamic vinegar","Dijon mustard","honey","parsley","feta cheese"]

Title: Egg Soup
Quantity: ["2 cups chicken broth", "1 tbsp cornstarch", "1 well beaten egg", "2 tbsp sliced green onion"]
RecipeMethod: ["In saucepan slowly stir the chicken broth into cornstarch. Cook, stirring constantly, until slightly thickened.", "Slowly pour in the well beaten egg; stir once gently.", "Remove from heat. Garnish with sliced green onion.", "Makes 4 servings."]

Title: Turkey Chili
Quantity: ["1 pound ground turkey","15 oz black beans","15 oz kidney beans","15 oz diced tomatoes","1 cup chopped onion","1 cup chopped bell pepper","2 cloves garlic, minced","1 tablespoon chili powder","1 teaspoon cumin","1/4 teaspoon cayenne pepper","Salt and pepper","1 cup water","1 tablespoon olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.","Add ground turkey and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.","Add onions, bell peppers, and garlic to the pot and cook until softened.","Stir in the chili powder, cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper.","Add the beans, tomatoes, and water to the pot and stir to combine.","Bring the mixture to a simmer and let cook for 30-45 minutes.","Serve hot with toppings of your choice, such as shredded cheese, avocado, or cilantro."]
Ingredients: ["turkey","black beans","kidney beans","tomato","onion","bell pepper","garlic","chili powder","cumin","cayenne pepper","Salt and pepper","water","olive oil"]

Title: Grilled Veggie Burger
Quantity: ["1/2 cup cooked quinoa","1 can black beans, drained and rinsed","1/2 red onion, finely chopped","1/2 red bell pepper, finely chopped","1 garlic clove, minced","1 tsp ground cumin","1 tsp smoked paprika","1/4 tsp salt","1/4 tsp black pepper","1/4 cup breadcrumbs","1 egg","4 whole wheat hamburger buns","4 slices of tomato","4 lettuce leaves"]
RecipeMethod: ["Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.","In a large bowl, mash the black beans with a fork or potato masher until they are mostly broken up.","Add cooked quinoa, red onion, red bell pepper, garlic, cumin, smoked paprika, salt, black pepper, breadcrumbs, and egg. Mix well.","Divide the mixture into 4 equal portions and shape each portion into a patty.","Grill the patties for 4-5 minutes on each side, or until browned and heated through.","Toast the buns lightly on the grill.","Assemble the burgers with a patty, tomato slice, lettuce leaf, and any additional toppings you prefer.","Serve immediately."]
Ingredients: ["quinoa","black beans","red onion","red bell pepper","garlic clove","ground cumin","smoked paprika","salt","black pepper","breadcrumbs","egg","whole wheat hamburger buns","tomato","lettuce leaves"]

Title: Cilantro Lime Shrimp with Quinoa
Quantity: ["1 lb shrimp, peeled and deveined","1 cup quinoa","2 cups chicken broth","1/4 cup freshly squeezed lime juice","1/4 cup chopped cilantro","2 tbsp olive oil","2 cloves garlic, minced","1 tsp honey","Salt and pepper, to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["Rinse quinoa thoroughly in a fine mesh strainer and drain well.In a medium saucepan, bring the water or chicken broth to a boil over high heat. Add the quinoa, reduce heat to low, cover and simmer until the water is absorbed, about 15-20 minutes.","In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, cilantro, olive oil, garlic, honey, salt, and pepper.","In a large bowl, combine cooked quinoa and shrimp. Pour the lime-cilantro mixture over the quinoa and shrimp, and toss to coat.","Heat a non-stick skillet over medium-high heat. Add the shrimp mixture and cook until the shrimp are pink and opaque, about 2-3 minutes per side.","Serve hot and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["shrimp","quinoa","chicken broth","lime juice","chopped cilantro","olive oil","garlic","honey","Salt and pepper"]

Title: Chickpea and Quinoa Salad
Quantity: ["1 cup quinoa, rinsed and drained","2 cups water","1 can chickpeas, drained and rinsed","1 red bell pepper, diced","1 small red onion, diced","1/2 cup chopped fresh parsley","1/4 cup chopped fresh mint","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro","1/4 cup lemon juice","1/4 cup olive oil","1/2 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon black pepper"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a medium saucepan, bring the quinoa and water to a boil over high heat.","Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for about 15-20 minutes, or until the quinoa is tender and the water is absorbed.","Fluff the quinoa with a fork and let cool.","In a large bowl, combine the cooled quinoa, chickpeas, red bell pepper, red onion, parsley, mint, and cilantro.","In a small bowl, whisk together the lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and black pepper.","Drizzle the dressing over the salad and toss to combine.","Serve chilled."]
Ingredients: ["quinoa","chickpeas","red bell pepper","red onion","parsley","fresh mint","cilantro","lemon juice","olive oil","salt","black pepper"]

Title: Vegetable omelette with mushrooms, peppers, onions, and a sprinkle of low-fat cheese
Quantity: ["2 large eggs","1/4 cup sliced mushrooms","1/4 cup diced red bell pepper","1/4 cup diced onion","1 tablespoon olive oil","1 tablespoon low-fat shredded cheese","Salt and black pepper to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a non-stick skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat.","Add the sliced mushrooms, diced red bell pepper, and diced onion to the skillet.","Saute the vegetables for 3-4 minutes, until they are tender and slightly browned.","In a bowl, beat the eggs with a pinch of salt and black pepper.","Pour the beaten eggs into the skillet with the vegetables.","Let the eggs cook for 2-3 minutes, until the bottom is set.","Sprinkle the shredded cheese on top of the omelette.","Using a spatula, fold the omelette in half and let it cook for another minute or two, until the cheese is melted and the eggs are cooked through.","Slide the omelette onto a plate and serve."]
Ingredients: ["eggs","mushrooms","red bell pepper","onion","olive oil","low-fat shredded cheese","Salt and black pepper to taste"]

Title: Greek Yogurt with Berries
Quantity: ["1 cup plain Greek yogurt","1/2 cup mixed berries ","1 tablespoon honey"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a bowl, add the Greek yogurt.","In a bowl, add the Greek yogurt.","Add the mixed berries on top of the Greek yogurt.","Drizzle honey on top of the berries."]

Title: Chia seed pudding with sliced bananas and a sprinkle of cinnamon
Quantity: ["1/4 cup chia seeds","1 cup unsweetened almond milk","1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract","1 tablespoon honey (optional)","1/2 medium banana, sliced","A sprinkle of cinnamon"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a bowl, mix the chia seeds, unsweetened almond milk, vanilla extract, and honey (if using) until well combined.","Cover the bowl and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight, until the mixture has thickened and the chia seeds have absorbed the liquid.","Once the chia seed pudding has set, spoon it into a bowl or jar.","Add the sliced banana on top of the chia seed pudding.","Sprinkle cinnamon over the banana and chia seed pudding.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Avocado Toast
Quantity: ["2 slices of whole wheat bread","1 avocado, mashed","4 egg whites","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1/4 teaspoon garlic powder","1 tablespoon olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["Toast the whole wheat bread and set aside.","In a small bowl, whisk the egg whites, salt, black pepper, and garlic powder together.,"Heat the olive oil in a non-stick pan over medium heat.","Pour the egg mixture into the pan and scramble the eggs until they are fully cooked.","Spread the mashed avocado on each slice of toast.","Top each slice of toast with the scrambled egg whites.","Add optional toppings like sliced cherry tomatoes, chopped cilantro, and hot sauce.","Serve and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: [" whole wheat bread","avocado","egg whites","salt","black pepper","garlic powder","olive oil"]

Title: Vegetarian Curry
Quantity: ["1 cup brown rice","1 tbsp olive oil","1 onion, chopped","3 garlic cloves, minced","2 tbsp curry powder","1 tbsp ground cumin","1 tsp ground coriander","1/4 tsp cayenne pepper","1 can (15 oz) chickpeas","1 can (14.5 oz) diced tomatoes","1 can (14 oz) light coconut milk","2 cups chopped vegetables (such as zucchini, bell peppers, and carrots)","Salt and pepper to taste","Chopped fresh cilantro, for serving"]
RecipeMethod: ["Cook the brown rice according to package instructions.","In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat. Add the onion and garlic and sauté until tender, about 5 minutes.","Add the curry powder, cumin, coriander, and cayenne pepper to the skillet and stir until fragrant, about 1 minute.","Add the chickpeas, diced tomatoes, coconut milk, and chopped vegetables to the skillet.","Stir well to combine.","Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat and simmer until the vegetables are tender, about 20 minutes.","Season with salt and pepper to taste.","Serve the curry over brown rice, garnished with chopped cilantro."]
Ingredients: ["brown rice","olive oil","onion","garlic","curry powder","cumin","coriander","cayenne pepper","chickpeas","tomato","light coconut milk","chopped vegetables","Salt and pepper"]

Title: Tofu scramble with spinach, mushrooms, and onions
Quantity: ["8 oz firm tofu, drained and crumbled","1 cup fresh spinach leaves","1/2 cup sliced mushrooms","1/4 cup diced onions","1 garlic clove, minced","1/2 teaspoon turmeric","1/2 teaspoon paprika","Salt and pepper to taste","1 teaspoon olive oil"]
RecipeMethod: ["Heat the olive oil in a skillet over medium-high heat.","Add the onions and garlic to the skillet and sauté for 2-3 minutes, or until the onions are translucent.","Add the sliced mushrooms to the skillet and sauté for 2-3 minutes, or until the mushrooms are tender.","Add the crumbled tofu to the skillet and stir to combine with the vegetables.","Add the turmeric, paprika, salt, and pepper to the skillet and stir to evenly coat the tofu and vegetables with the spices.","Cook for 5-7 minutes, or until the tofu is slightly browned and the vegetables are cooked.","Add the spinach to the skillet and stir to combine with the tofu and vegetables.","Cook for another 2-3 minutes, or until the spinach is wilted.","Serve and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["tofu","spinach","mushrooms","onions","garlic clove","turmeric","paprika","Salt and pepper to taste","olive oil"]

Title: Peanut Butter and Banana Smoothie
Quantity: ["1 frozen banana","1/2 cup unsweetened almond milk","1 tbsp natural peanut butter","1 scoop vanilla protein powder","1 tbsp chia seeds"]
RecipeMethod: ["Add frozen banana, almond milk, peanut butter, protein powder, and chia seeds to a blender and blend until smooth.","Pour the mixture into a bowl and add toppings of your choice."]
Ingredients: ["banana","unsweetened almond milk","peanut butter","vanilla protein powder","chia seeds"]

Title: Fried Cabbage
Quantity: ["1 head cabbage", "1 onion", "1 bell pepper", "1 tomato", "2 tbsp sugar", "1 tsp salt", "1 tsp pepper"]
RecipeMethod: ["Chop or cut up in small pieces; let stand at least 1 hour. Put 3 tablespoons of oil in skillet and heat.", "Drain vegetables. Put in skillet.", "Add 1/2 cup water and cook 20 or 30 minutes."]

Title: Breakfast Burrito
Quantity: ["2 large flour tortillas","4 large eggs","1/4 cup shredded cheddar cheese","1/4 cup diced ham","1/4 cup diced green bell pepper","1/4 cup diced onion","2 tablespoons olive oil","Salt and pepper, to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat","Add diced onion and green bell pepper and sauté until softened.","Add diced ham to the skillet and cook for a few minutes.","In a separate bowl, whisk together eggs and pour them into the skillet.","Scramble the eggs with the ham and vegetables until cooked through.","Warm the tortillas in the microwave or on a skillet.","Divide the egg mixture evenly between the tortillas.","Sprinkle shredded cheddar cheese over the top of the egg mixture.","Roll the tortillas up tightly to form burritos.","Serve immediately."]
Ingredients: ["tortillas","eggs","cheddar cheese","ham","green bell pepper","onion","olive oil","Salt and pepper"]

Title: Grilled chicken breast with sliced tomatoes and cucumber
Quantity: ["1 boneless, skinless chicken breast","1/2 medium tomato, sliced","1/2 medium cucumber, sliced","1 tablespoon olive oil","Salt and black pepper to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["Season the chicken breast with salt and black pepper on both sides.",Place the chicken breast on the grill or grill pan and cook for 4-5 minutes","Arrange the sliced tomato and cucumber on a plate.","Place the sliced chicken breast on top of the vegetables.","Serve and enjoy!"]

Title: Corn and Egg Scramble
Quantity: ["1 can corn", "4 egg, beaten", "1 tbsp olive oil", "1 tsp pepper", "1/2 tsp salt"]
RecipeMethod: ["Heat oil in a 10-inch nonstick skillet over medium.", "Add corn and cook, stirring often, until slightly browned.", "Add peppers and cook, stirring constantly.",  "Add eggs and scramble"]

Title: Loaded Omelete
Quantity: ["2 large eggs","1/4 cup shredded cheddar cheese","1/4 cup diced ham","1/4 cup diced bell peppers","1/4 cup diced onion","1 tablespoon olive oil","Salt and pepper to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a small bowl, whisk together the eggs with salt and pepper.","Heat the olive oil in a non-stick skillet over medium heat.","Add the diced onions and bell peppers and sauté for 2-3 minutes, until they start to soften.","Add the diced ham to the skillet and cook for another 1-2 minutes.","Pour the whisked eggs into the skillet and cook until set, about 2-3 minutes.","Sprinkle the shredded cheddar cheese on top of the omelette and fold it in half.","Cook for another minute or so until the cheese is melted"]
Ingredients: ["eggs","cheddar cheese","diced ham","bell peppers","onion","olive oil","Salt and pepper to taste"]

Title: Bagel with Cream Cheese and Smoked Salmon
Quantity: ["1 bagel, sliced and toasted", "2 tbsp cream cheese", "2 oz smoked salmon", "1 tbsp chopped fresh chives", "1 slice of red onion", "1 slice of tomato"]
RecipeMethod: ["Spread the cream cheese evenly over the toasted bagel slices. Top with smoked salmon, red onion, tomato, and chopped chives. Serve and enjoy!"]
Ingredients: ["1 bagel, sliced and toasted", "2 tbsp cream cheese", "2 oz smoked salmon", "1 tbsp chopped fresh chives", "1 slice of red onion", "1 slice of tomato"]

Title: Chicken and Egg Sandwich
Quantity: ["2 slices of whole wheat bread","1 grilled chicken breast, sliced","2 hard boiled eggs","1/2 avocado","1 small tomato, sliced","1 leaf of lettuce","Salt and pepper to taste"]
RecipeMethod: ["Toast the bread to your preference.","Layer the chicken slices on one slice of bread.","Layer the egg slices on top of the chicken.","Add avocado slices and tomato slices.","Top with a leaf of lettuce.","Sprinkle salt and pepper to taste.","Cover with the other slice of bread and enjoy!"]

Title: Indian Fried Bread
Quantity: ["1 cup flour", "1 tsp baking powder", "1/2 tsp salt", "1 cup milk"]
RecipeMethod: ["Make a soft dough, using the first 3 ingredients and a little shortening.", "Add enough milk to mix; cut this together.", "Drop by spoonfuls into hot grease; let fry until brown and crisp.", "Serve hot."]

Title: Protein Pancakes
Quantity: ["1 cup oat flour","1 scoop vanilla protein powder","1/2 tsp baking powder","1/4 tsp salt","1/2 cup almond milk","2 egg whites","1/2 tsp vanilla extract","Cooking spray"]
RecipeMethod: ["In a mixing bowl, combine oat flour, protein powder, baking powder, and salt.","In a separate bowl, whisk together almond milk, egg whites, and vanilla extract.", "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and stir until well combined.","Heat a non-stick pan or griddle over medium heat and lightly coat with cooking spray.","Pour 1/4 cup of batter onto the pan for each pancake.","Cook until the edges begin to dry and the surface begins to bubble.","Flip and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes until lightly browned.","Repeat with remaining batter.","Serve with your choice of toppings, such as fresh fruit, nuts, or a drizzle of honey."]

Title: Salsa
Quantity: ["6 tomatoes, diced", "4 oz chopped green chilies", "1/2 cup green onions, chopped", "1 1/2 cup celery, finely diced", "2 medium yellow onions, chopped", "1 cup chopped parsley", "15 oz tomato paste", "1 tsp cumin", "1 tsp garlic", "1 tsp salt", "1 tsp pepper"]

Title: Nut Cookies

Title: Cheese Cake

Title: Biscuits

Title: Almond Chicken And Rice Casserole

Title: Mexican Chicken
